{
  "id": "adv_bond_kan_01_02",
  "title": "kana2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "ここが最近東京に進出してきた、人気のパフェ屋さん？\n先週オープンしたにしては店内に人が少ないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is this a popular parfait shop that recently opened in Tokyo?\nThere aren't many people inside‚ considering it just opened last week",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、でも「これからブレイクする」ネタを\n選んでSNSに載せるのがプロってもんよねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ but‚ choosing the topic 'Taking a break now'\nand posting it on SNS is what it means to be a pro",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6182539304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.6555553437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "ま、すぐにkanaの投稿で\n行列になるだろうけど……ん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ there'll be a line for\nkana's post soon… huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6555553437,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.0563036125
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、kanaさんじゃないですかぁ～\nはっ！？　まさかこころに会いたくてつけて来た……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ isn't that kana-san~\nOh!? Could it be that you came here because you wanted to see Kokoro…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.0563036125,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 277.02972080000166
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6626755239
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "……ちっ。よりにもよって、あんたの隣の席とか\nなんでオフの日までムカつく顔見ないといけないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hold on. Of all places‚ right next you‚\nwhy do I have to see that annoying face even on my day off",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6626755239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.8666662695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "お～怖い顔～。kanaさんも、ここのパフェを食べに\n来たんですよね？　SNSのネタにしようと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh~ A scary face~. kana-san‚ you came here to eat parfait too\nright? You're thinking of making it into a SNS topic",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8666662695,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 49.4709970317
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　せっかく会ったんですし「一緒にパフェ\n食べました」って、SNSにアップしませんかぁ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! Since we last met\nwhy don't we post on SNS‚ 'We ate parfait together'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4709970317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.3115183038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "絶対イヤ。なんでkanaからあんたのアカウントに\nフォロワー流してあげないといけないわけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely not. Why should kana\nsend followers to your account?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3115183038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0911329112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "え～、先輩との仲良しアピールですよ～？\nウケますよ？　話題になること間違いなしですよ～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~‚ is this just to show off how close you are with senpai~?\nIt's a cool? It'll definitely be a hot topic~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0911329112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.7776411218
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "先輩との仲良しアピールならリズノワのやつらと\nやっとけ。kanaはあんたの先輩じゃないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you want to show off your friendship with your senpai‚ do it with guys\nfrom LizNoir. kana isn't your senpai",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7776411218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.024398788
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　先輩じゃないことくらい知ってます\n星見プロではkanaさんがこころの後輩ですもんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah? I know you're not my senpai\nAt Hoshimi Prods‚ kana is Kokoro's kohai‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.024398788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.7666212561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "このクソガキ！　芸歴はこっちのが遙かに上だっての\nそんなのやりたきゃ、さくらにでも声掛けるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You little brat! My career is much higher than yours\nIf you want to say something like that‚ go tell Sakura",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7666212561,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.1764851413
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "お！　こころのパフェが到着しました～\nおお～、間近で見るとかなりの迫力……迫力……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Kokoro's parfait has arrived~\nWow~‚ it's so impressive up close… so impressive…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.1764851413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "え、デカくない……？　写真では分からなかったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ isn't it big…? I didn't know from the picture‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6355554424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.6355554424
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "思ってたよりだいぶ量あるな。さすがに一人じゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it's a lot bigger than I thought. I guess I can do it alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "でっかい……ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It is… big…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.6377324266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.6377324266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころの小さな体に収まりきるかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it will fit into Kokoro's small body…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "写真だけ撮って残す人が多いって問題になってますし\nギブアップはあり得ません、あり得ませんけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Many people who just take pictures and leave them behind‚ so it's becoming a problem\nThere is no give-up‚ no give-up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4717821918,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1339135649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ\nkanaせんぱぁーい！　もうパフェ注文しましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes\nkana senpaiー! Have you already ordered your parfait?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1339135649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まだだよぉ～。ねえ、こころちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not yet~. Hey‚ Kokoro-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.9667479994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 144.9667479994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "お店混んできたし、そっちの席に移動してもいい～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shop is getting crowded‚ can I move to your seat~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "事務所の優しくて可愛い先輩と仲良く分け合って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You ate it with a beautiful and cute senpai from the agency‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6375187399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.6375187399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_kan_01_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "食べましたって、写真撮ってSNSに載せていいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "so you can take a picture and post it on SNS~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こころの方が先輩ですけど大人なので、どうしてもって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro is a senpai and more mature‚ if you insist‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6449559055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.6449559055
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
